{"tid":2103701,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"書展下周三舉行　張竹君籲參展商及顧客戴口罩","createTime":"2020-07-11T11:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T11:36:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"23a0f50bb3070adabf783f6c69f4c9f8a570f1b7","tid":2103701,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T11:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/event/1024/202006/20200626014949_0_20190708180346-0-hktdc-book-fair-2018-029.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Fevent%2F1024%2F202006%2F20200626014949_0_20190708180346-0-hktdc-book-fair-2018-029.jpg&h=84a49f18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港書展下周三舉行，衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君被問到如常舉行書展的衞生風險，她提醒參展商及顧客起碼要戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n另外，醫管局總行政經理何婉霞表示，再多有10人出院，另外有2人情況危殆、2人嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n她又表示，廣華醫院一名支援職系員工因為家人確診，被列為密切接觸者，會被安排入住檢疫中心。她表示，相關員工在醫院廚房工作，昨日有上班，本身沒有病徵，不需要接觸病人，廚房今日已徹底清潔。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537187-20200711.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537187-20200711.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyFGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=918ac324\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537187-20200711.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=822d666a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537187-20200711.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"7c649ee0f6d1d943f5e1191a1ffbccd527315cd4","tid":2103701,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T11:36:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">Corona Book Fair!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i